Package: streamFit
Type: Package
Title: Online Sequential Parameter Estimation for Streaming Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Georgios Vassos [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Georgios Vassos <georgios.vassos@example.com>
Description: Sequential online parameter estimation for generalised linear
    models and linear models via two complementary algorithms: Recursive Least
    Squares with Sherman-Morrison Fisher information updates (RLS-GLM,
    O(p^2) per step) and Implicit Stochastic Gradient Descent (iSGD,
    O(p) per step). Both algorithms support forgetting factors or adaptive
    learning rate schedules for tracking time-varying parameters. Reduces to
    standard weighted RLS for Gaussian responses. Compatible with any R
    family object (binomial, poisson, gaussian, etc.). Designed for
    extension to survival models, state-space models, and other streaming
    estimation problems.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/gvassos/streamFit
BugReports: https://github.com/gvassos/streamFit/issues
Imports:
